NK039(ti)017:1: // ma tshogs 'khor bcas bshags pa bgyi ba ni /
NK039(ti)017:3: 'gro ba'i don ched sku mchog 'jigs pa la //
NK039(ti)017:4: ma lus khyad par gsal bar mdzad pa yi //
NK039(ti)017:5: nga rgyal dregs pa thams cad 'dul mdzad pa //
NK039(ti)017:6: yon tan rdzogs pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)017:8: rdo rje rgyal po bde bar gshegs pa'i bdag /
NK039(ti)017:9: gsang sngags rnal 'byor mnyes pa'i grub pa mo //
NK039(ti)017:10: yon tan mang po'i 'gro ba'i don mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)017:11: sngon gyis las kyi 'brel ba'i bdag bzung ste //
NK039(ti)017:12: sku gsum sgyu mar bstan pa'i bka' drin che //
NK039(ti)017:13: dus ngan snyigs ma'i dus 'dir bdag skyes te //
NK039(ti)017:14: ma rig nyon mongs bag med dbang gyur te //
NK039(ti)017:15: dam tshig nyams shing thugs dang 'gal gyur pa //
NK039(ti)017:16: rdo rje dam ldan ma la bzod par gsol //
NK039(ti)017:18: ma mo dbyings phyug rdo rje rig ma la //
NK039(ti)017:19: log rtog gzhom phyir yum gyi tshul ston cing //
NK039(ti)017:20: khro bzhad lcang lor bcas pa'i cod pan can //
NK039(ti)017:21: yon tan ldan pa'i sku gsung thugs nyid la //
NK039(ti)017:22: ma rig dbang gis sgros dang bskur btab ste //
NK039(ti)017:23: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK039(ti)017:25: bder gshegs rgyal ba'i bstan pa rgyas mdzad cing /
NK039(ti)017:26: thams cad 'jigs tshul chas chen rnams kyi brgyan //
NK039(ti)017:27: dur khrod gnas pa'i bong bu zhabs kyi brten //
NK039(ti)017:28: dril chung phreng bas sku yi rgyan du byas //
NK039(ti)017:29: gsang bar dam bca' bu rnams kyis //
NK039(ti)017:30: sems can lag pas nyon mongs lnga rgyas pas //
NK039(ti)017:31: smin cing bsgrub par bya ba ma grub pas //
NK039(ti)017:32: ma cig me 'bar sku la bzod par gsol //
NK039(ti)017:34: d+ha ka rdo rje dam tshig gtan gyi gnyer //
NK039(ti)017:35: gsang bar dam bcas sku yi dam tshig las //
NK039(ti)017:36: sku yi spyod pa tshul bzhin ma rtogs te //
NK039(ti)017:37: le lo sems gnyis zos pa thams cad kun //
NK039(ti)017:38: bsgom dang bsgrub pa'i tshul bzhin ma bsrung ba //
NK039(ti)017:39: byams pa'i thugs rje g.yel bar gyur pa ni //
NK039(ti)017:40: khams gsum rgyal mo'i sku la h'u /
NK039(ti)017:41: ma cig bder gshegs rigs lnga dpal gyi yum //
NK039(ti)017:42: dus gsum rgyal ba thams cad bskyed pa'i ma //
NK039(ti)017:43: ci bzhin 'gro ba thams cad de 'dus pa'i //
NK039(ti)017:44: ma cig sprul pa'i sku h'u /
NK039(ti)017:46: spyi dang khyad par lhag pa'i dam tshig las //
NK039(ti)017:47: ma cig dam tshig rjes su mi btang yang //
NK039(ti)017:48: klong du ma gyur rtsal shugs goms chung bas //
NK039(ti)017:49: ma cig skyong ma'i sku la h'u /
NK039(ti)017:50: thugs rjes nges par gzigs pa'i yul rnams la //
NK039(ti)017:51: dam rdzas ma tshangs mchod pa ma bshams te //
NK039(ti)017:52: 'phang sems dbang gi mchod pa rgyu chung bas //
NK039(ti)017:53: rjid mo bkang bzlog sku h'u /
NK039(ti)017:54: ma cig sku mdog phyag mtshan phyag rgya las //
NK039(ti)017:55: don dang mthun par tshul bzhin ma rtogs te //
NK039(ti)017:56: 'phags pa'i thugs rjes g.yel bar gyur pa rnams //
NK039(ti)017:58: thams cad 'jigs tshul khro bzhad 'bar ba'i zhal //
NK039(ti)017:59: mdzes par rgyan ldan ko rlon sham thabs can //
NK039(ti)017:60: gdug pa'i tshogs 'dul sbrul gyis ske rag bcings //
NK039(ti)017:61: bu yi tshul du rgyun gyis dam tshig las //
NK039(ti)017:62: le lo yul thum bre mo'i gtam la sogs //
NK039(ti)017:63: thugs dang 'gal bar gyur pa ci mchis pa //
NK039(ti)017:64: thams cad ma lus byams pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK039(ti)017:65: ma cig thugs rjes tshangs pa rtsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)017:67: rnal 'byor ma yi dam tshig 'dzin pa rnams //
NK039(ti)017:68: bu yi tshul gyi thams cad bsrung ba dang //
NK039(ti)017:69: zhe sdang gdug pa'i dgra bgegs gang byung yang //
NK039(ti)017:70: ma cig thugs rjes lhag par der phyung zhing //
NK039(ti)017:71: drag shul zhi rgyas dbang dang mngon spyod kyis //
NK039(ti)017:72: thams cad ma lus rdzogs par phrin las mdzod //
NK039(ti)017:74: thugs brtser ldan pa'i rdo rje rdzong mo la //
NK039(ti)017:75: 'di skad bshags shing gsol bar 'tshams pa dang //
NK039(ti)017:76: nyon mongs thal ba'i sems kyi ma bshags te //
NK039(ti)017:77: 'gro don byang chub sems kyi bshags gyur te //
NK039(ti)017:78: thugs dang 'gal bar ci mchis bzod par gsol //
NK039(ti)017:79: re zhing smon pa yid bzhin 'grub gyur cig /
NK039(ti)017:81: rdo rje las kyi sring mo bong zhon ma //
NK039(ti)017:82: ye nas rang bzhin dag pa'i sku bzhugs kyang //
NK039(ti)017:83: rnal 'byor bdag 'dra'i sems kyi bag chags skyen rnams sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK039(ti)017:84: 'dod khams skyong ma'i gtso mo khyod la bzod par gsol //
NK039(ti)017:85: gdung ba drag pos sems kyi shugs phyung nas //
NK039(ti)017:86: nga ro drag pos ngu zhing mchi ma bsil //
NK039(ti)017:87: nyams gril mchis pa rnal 'byor yongs su smre //
NK039(ti)017:88: 'dod khams lha mo khyed la smre gsol lo //
NK039(ti)017:90: thod pa dgu brtsegs srid pa'i gzhal yas nas //
NK039(ti)017:91: dpal ldan lha mo gsan cing dgongs su gsol //
NK039(ti)017:92: rang la rig pa'i ye shes rgyud ldan yang //
NK039(ti)017:93: 'phral byung log rtog shin tu 'bang che bas //
NK039(ti)017:94: ma yi thugs dang 'gal bar bzod gshin rje ye nas lha mo'i khyod yin kyang //
NK039(ti)017:95: phrag dog dbang gis bgyis pa bzod rlung nag ye nas lha mo'i sprul yin kyang //
NK039(ti)017:96: log par bltas te ma dad bzod bong bu ye nas lha mo'i bcibs yin yang //
NK039(ti)017:97: ma brten brdeg par gyur par bzod nal ma ye nas lha mo'i grogs yin yang //
NK039(ti)017:98: log par bltas te gshe ba bzod nal bu'i ye nas lha mo'i sras yin yang //
NK039(ti)017:99: ma brten bskrad par gyur par yug sa ye nas lha mo'i dgra yin yang //
NK039(ti)017:100: 'dod chags dbang gis spyod par bzod phag rdzi ye nas lha mo khyod yin yang //
NK039(ti)017:101: ma brten bskrad par gyur par 'gar ba ye nas lha mo'i dgra yin yang //
NK039(ti)017:102: ma bskrad brten par gyur par bdag cag ye nas ser sna'i dbang gyur pas //
NK039(ti)017:103: mchod tshogs gtor ma zhan pa bzod le lo snyam las dbang du gyur lags pas //
NK039(ti)017:104: mchod pa lo zlar 'das pa bzod gtor ma dus
NK039(ti)017:105: la g.yel ba bzod gcom la phyar bas man ngag
NK039(ti)017:106: gsang ma thub // zab mo'i thugs dang 'gal ba bzod kyee /
NK039(ti)017:107: gsang sngags zab mo'i tshogs rnams dgongs su gsol //
NK039(ti)017:108: ma dang mkha' 'gro srung ma dam tshig can //
NK039(ti)017:109: thams cad ma lus bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK039(ti)017:110: rdo rje slob dpon dam tshig mched la sogs //
NK039(ti)017:111: bdag la dam tshig bzhin du dgongs su gsol //
NK039(ti)017:112: bdag gis thog ma med pa'i dus mtha' nas //
NK039(ti)017:113: chos nyid ye nas mnyam pa chen po la //
NK039(ti)017:114: bdag blo rmongs pas de ltar ma rtogs te //
NK039(ti)017:115: kun rdzob rtog pa'i bag chags rjes 'brang nas //
NK039(ti)017:116: chos dang mi mthun rnam smin sna tshogs bsags //
NK039(ti)017:117: byams mgon thugs rje'i thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK039(ti)017:118: rgyal ba rgyal mtsho'i tshogs la bzod par bzhes nas tshangs par rtsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)017:119: le lo'i dbang gis bsgom bsgrub las la g.yel //
NK039(ti)017:120: yi dam lha tshogs tshul bzhin ma bsgom pas //
NK039(ti)017:121: gsang sngags lha tshogs thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK039(ti)017:122: yi dam zhi khro'i tshogs la bzod sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub bdag la stsol //
NK039(ti)017:123: dam rdzas ma tshang lha mo ma brnyes pas //
NK039(ti)017:124: dbyings phyug rgyal mo'i tshul bzhin ma brten pas //
NK039(ti)017:125: rang byung rgyal mo'i thugs 'dod khams dbang phyug la ser sna'i dbang gi slob dpon thugs dang 'gal //
NK039(ti)017:126: chos bzhin ma lcog gzung 'dzin dbang du gyur //
NK039(ti)017:127: rdo rje slob dpon thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK039(ti)017:128: phrin las chen po'i sku la zhe sdang dbang gi gzhan la gnod sems bskyed //
NK039(ti)017:129: nyon mongs dbang gi rdo rje mched dang 'gal //
NK039(ti)017:130: mched dang lcam dral dam tshig gzung ma la //
NK039(ti)017:131: gti mug dbang gyur 'gal ba'i las bgyis pa //
NK039(ti)017:132: mi ldog dam ldan sku la bzod par gsol //
NK039(ti)017:133: bzod par bzhes nas tshangs pa stsal du gsol //
